"Examples of using the canvas API"
"Requires that the Canvas object already exist."

META Canvas
setup: testName
  "Set up a canvas in a window"
  | w c b |
  w <- self window: testName.
  c <- self create: 'canvas'.
  b <- self button: 'close' action: [w remove].
  w append: c.
  w append: b.
  ^ c
!

